### Test API Endpoints

### 1. Đăng ký User thường
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "user1@example.com"
}

### 2. Đăng ký Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "admin1@example.com"
}

### 3. Đăng nhập User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Đăng nhập Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. Test User Profile (cần JWT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6. Test User Dashboard (cần JWT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 7. Test Admin Dashboard (cần JWT token của admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Test Admin Users (cần JWT token của admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Test Menu Items (public endpoint)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/items

### 10. Test Orders API (cần JWT token)
# Test authentication
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/test-auth
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

# Tạo order mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "size": "medium",
  "shippingAddress": "123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789"
}

# Lấy danh sách orders của user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/user
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

# Lấy tất cả orders (admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# Cập nhật status order
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=SHIPPING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Variables (sử dụng trong VS Code REST Client extension):
# userToken: JWT token từ đăng nhập user
# adminToken: JWT token từ đăng nhập admin
